              <span id="reviewTextContainer3579141113" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11815904131937676111">Another entertaining and atmospheric Montalbano novel, well narrated by Grover Gardner in the audiobook format. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

